  "texts": [
    "Moreover, our methodology permits researchers to concentrate on studies within their area of interest.",
    "By applying the OR command, the search query's scope is broadened to encompass any studies with one or more of the query keywords in their title or abstract, while the AND command ensures relevance to the field of study.",
    "This methodology guarantees that all relevant studies are identified and included in the review.",
    "As of December 31 st, 2023, we identified 1612 and 3775 records in the WoS and Scopus databases, respectively.",
    "We limited the search to articles published in English in the last ten years between 2013 and 2023."
